
BAIXADO E EXECUTANDO CONTAINER USANDO COMANDO PULL

docker image pull redis:latest

COMANDO BASICOS

docker image pull
docker image ls
docker image inspect
docker image tag <imagem de Origem> <tag>
docker image build
docker image push


